 gold? Well, that depends if you find someone who loans you money against y=
our collateral, that is someone who is unaffected by sanctions and loans yo=
u against collateral you couldn=E2=80=99t sell in a liquid market and which=
 sits in a vault in Moscow.If Vladimir Putin came to you and asked to borro=
w $1 billion, saying =E2=80=9Cdon=E2=80=99t worry, as collateral, I will gi=
ve you ownership of $1.1 billion of gold that I will hang on to for you in =
a vault in Moscow,=E2=80=9D would you give him the money?
