. But =E2=80=9Cbank loses money due to oligarch yacht loans=E2=80=9D is ter=
rible! Terrible! You can=E2=80=99t do that!So you do a trade where Credit S=
uisse makes the oligarch yacht loans, for branding and relationship and bus=
iness development purposes, and as far as the oligarchs are concerned it is=
